{"tid":2212779,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"制裁陰霾下 聶德權兩子向花旗承按","createTime":"2020-09-22T05:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T08:08:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7da1d15a6d0a92f987d3000787e1134de14477","tid":2212779,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200922/RKT6TQ7G4BENTCRQ6BAPV64CCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200922%2FRKT6TQ7G4BENTCRQ6BAPV64CCM%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEdT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=2e72869e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200922%2FRKT6TQ7G4BENTCRQ6BAPV64CCM%2F&h=a7c4528b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200922/RKT6TQ7G4BENTCRQ6BAPV64CCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n制裁陰霾下 聶德權兩子向花旗承按<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u_5ZMC4O22kPMT16sie9UAPsy5Q=/709x655/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PDU65CNSTFEZZJGI62446OI22M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu_5ZMC4O22kPMT16sie9UAPsy5Q%3D%2F709x655%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPDU65CNSTFEZZJGI62446OI22M.gif&h=a45f1baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】11名中港官員被美國制裁，名單之一的律政司長鄭若驊及警務處長鄧炳強，先後還清其渣打及滙豐的按揭，鄧炳強更將按揭轉至中銀香港。根據本報查冊，不在制裁名單上的公務員事務局長聶德權，其中兩名兒子去年以首置名義買入的匯璽單位，今年8月「上會」，並以美資花旗銀行（香港）承造按揭，無懼中美關係惡化。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，聶德權及妻子張翠蘭的兒子聶天澄及聶天朗，於去年9月26日各自買入匯璽一個單位，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在兩人買入匯璽物業後，聶德權於去年10月初知會行會秘書處更新利益申報紀錄，新增該兩個物業，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各藉首置名義買匯璽單位<br />\n<br />\n翻查匯璽成交紀錄冊，聶天澄及聶天朗去年入市時，採用210天成交期付款計劃，理論上可在新按保計劃下借足九成按揭。不過，兩個單位目前同為無限額按揭，外界未能得知其實際按揭金額。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權長子聶天樂，早於2018年9月買入匯璽II單位，並透過滙豐銀行承造按揭。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權及妻子現持有沙田曉翠山莊低層B室連車位物業，亦是聶天澄及聶天朗買樓時之登記地址，。。。。。"},{"pid":"a4073527812dc4557d97ca9f36231207b9115167","tid":2212779,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc1e714b6d1be0f0dcd59a49cb31f8d9ff36c38","tid":2212779,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cbe211a7f965015d7e16c37e20e956705324d1","tid":2212779,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"他們只是孩子啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392f15e9896e93ab2ebf7bcf25099e2232d9eb8a","tid":2212779,"uid":14422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"佢個仔做測量顧問狗，畢咗業冇耐，搵二萬蚊，佢老豆借佢仔個名買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f1ba08579f7b9bc698967d310795f811c60483","tid":2212779,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"392f15e9896e93ab2ebf7bcf25099e2232d9eb8a","tid":2212779,"uid":14422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"佢個仔做測量顧問狗，畢咗業冇耐，搵二萬蚊，佢老豆借佢仔個名買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"佢個仔個樣成個大粒墨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c